{"type":"text","timestamp":1778978905131,"sessionID":"ses_1cc98b089ffeqDgg64MacYW8kG","part":{"id":"prt_e3367c565001JD4k8gGRmKiYBG","messageID":"msg_e3367b650001ERaOeEbMBlw4Jm","sessionID":"ses_1cc98b089ffeqDgg64MacYW8kG","type":"text","text":"The issue evolved in comments: `antimesosalpinx` already exists, and the latest curator guidance broadens this to eight regional tissue-layer terms. I’m now checking whether any of those seven remaining terms already exist and whether a simple `part_of` pattern is enough.","time":{"start":1778978899301,"end":1778978905128}}}
