M.D., Ph.D.](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/authors?id=539&pap=5)\n\n**Editorial Board Members:** [David B. Chapel, M.D.](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/authors?id=750&pap=3), Stephanie L. Skala, M.D.\n\n[![Brandon Douglas Metcalf, M.D.](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/pathout_uploads/2024/2/thumbs/20240212-143452_brandonmetcalf.png)](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/authors?id=1854&pap=5 \"Brandon Douglas Metcalf, M.D.\")\n\n[![Gulisa Turashvili, M.D., Ph.D.](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/pathout_uploads/2026/3/thumbs/20260317-084648_Turashvili.png)](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/authors?id=539&pap=5 \"Gulisa Turashvili, M.D., Ph.D.\")\n\n  \n\n**Last author update:** 30 July 2024\n\n**Last staff update:** 30 July 2024\n\n  \n\n[![Brandon Douglas Metcalf, M.D.](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/pathout_uploads/2024/2/thumbs/20240212-143452_brandonmetcalf.png)](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/authors?id=1854&pap=5 \"Brandon Douglas Metcalf, M.D.\")\n\n[![Gulisa Turashvili, M.D., Ph.D.](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/pathout_uploads/2026/3/thumbs/20260317-084648_Turashvili.png)](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/authors?id=539&pap=5 \"Gulisa Turashvili, M.D., Ph.D.\")\n\n**Copyright:** 2002-2026, PathologyOutlines.com, Inc.  \n  \n**PubMed Search:** [Fallopian tubes anatomy and histology](?term=Fallopian+tubes%5Btitle%5D+anatomy+and+histology+free+full+text%5BSB%5D)\n\n**Page views in 2025:** 20,331\n\n**Page views in 2026 to date:** 7,866\n\nTable of Contents\n\n[Definition / general](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/topic/fallopiantubesnormal.html#definitiongeneral506558) | [Essential features](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/topic/fallopiantubesnormal.html#essentialfeatures506559) | [Terminology](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/topic/fallopiantubesnormal.html#terminology506560) | [Physiology](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/topic/fallopiantubesnormal.html#physiology506561) | [Diagrams / tables](https://www.pathologyoutlines.com/topic/f